  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Service Health Monitoring",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# Service Health Monitoring (Phase 2C)\n\nProactive monitoring dashboard for service health:\n- **Activity**: Which services are producing logs\n- **Errors**: Service error rates and frequencies\n- **Restarts**: Service start/stop patterns\n- **Volume**: Log volume trends per service\n\n**Use Case**: Detect service degradation, track restart patterns, identify unhealthy services before failures occur"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total Services Active (7d)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "count(count by (service_name) (count_over_time({log_source=\"rsyslog_syslog\", service_name=~\"$service\"}[7d])))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Services with Errors (7d)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "count(count by (service_name) (count_over_time({level=\"error\", service_name=~\"$service\"}[7d])))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Avg Error Rate",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "avg(sum by (service_name) (rate(count_over_time({level=\"error\", service_name=~\"$service\"}[5m])[5m:1m])))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Services (current hour)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "count(count by (service_name) (count_over_time({log_source=\"rsyslog_syslog\", service_name=~\"$service\"}[1h])))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 18,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Log Volume per Service (7d)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (service_name) (rate(count_over_time({log_source=\"rsyslog_syslog\", service_name=~\"$service\"}[1h])[7d:1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ service_name }}"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error Rate per Service (7d)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (service_name) (rate(count_over_time({level=\"error\", service_name=~\"$service\"}[1h])[7d:1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ service_name }}"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 7,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Service Summary (7d)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(30, sum by (service_name) (count_over_time({log_source=\"rsyslog_syslog\", service_name=~\"$service\"}[7d])))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
